{"id": "work_97e3b5d3-9c94-5f22-9075-ed4718b1f53c", "title": "Approaching Unit Visibility for Control of a Superconducting Qubit with Dispersive Readout", "sources": [{"source": "dtic", "id": "pub.1013103968"}], "last_updated": "2026-03-09T19:36:32.272750", "abstract": "In a Rabi oscillation experiment with a superconducting qubit we show that a visibility in the qubit excited state population of more than 95% can be attained. We perform a dispersive measurement of the qubit state by coupling the qubit non-resonantly to a transmission line resonator and probing the resonator transmission spectrum. The measurement process is well characterized and quantitatively understood. In a measurement of Ramsey fringes, the qubit coherence time is larger than 500 ns.", "publication_date": "2005-08-01", "doi": "10.1103/physrevlett.95.060501", "url": "https://dtic.dimensions.ai/details/publication/pub.1013103968?and_facet_researcher=ur.015527265674.84", "citation_count": 0, "authors": [{"author_id": "author_db786820-6a2a-52d0-95c5-06b2dd7ce5d2", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_78542dd0-c538-5434-8d2c-fe6f77c8cde3", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_81b401fb-046a-541b-9444-170c08ed2c77", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_d2b8b900-5488-5f87-ab9d-06fb3b0ff50b", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_afd64421-6c30-5068-bae3-76e1ddd1daee", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_f3887ae3-1997-5c7c-bacd-477f516abf7d", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_05d4b046-8319-56cd-a216-425dff836a4f", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_b7f874c0-f80b-59b0-ae92-d836f62f2b84", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}], "orgs": [{"org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df", "role": "affiliation"}], "topics": [{"topic_id": "topic_40c92d30-1e13-51c2-a6bc-692493c876ff", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_7ced97ac-1108-5195-b3a2-d664e9eb9af5", "score": 1.0}], "created_at": "2026-03-09T19:36:32.272750"}